div.h2: Per-Process Page Directory Kernel Shared / User Isolated
div.p: PDE[0-767]: User-specific mappings (PTE_USER=1) PDE[768-1023]: Shared kernel PTEs (PTE_USER=0)
Any modification to these page tables is immediately visible to ALL processes they share the same physical PT frames. No TLB shootdown needed (single-core M3/M4).
Different physical frames per process. PTE_USER = 1 ring-3 can read/write. Ring-0 can always access (CPL DPL).
